Export compliance

PortBay contains standard, published encryption (TLS via rustls, SSH via
russh, locally generated development certificates). The notification for
publicly available encryption source code required by 15 CFR §742.15(b) of
the U.S. Export Administration Regulations was submitted to BIS
(crypt@bis.doc.gov) and NSA (enc@nsa.gov) on 2026-06-05. Under
15 CFR §734.3(b)(3) and §734.7(b), this source code and the binaries built
from it are not subject to the EAR.

